=== v1.2 ===
- Full code refactoring
- Converted to Swift 4.2
- Availability for iOS 8+
- Added a lot of new animations such as:
    - none
    - flipFromLeft
    - flipFromRight
    - flipFromBottom
    - curlUp
    - curlDown
    - zoomOut
    - zoomIn
    - sliceVertical
    - sliceHorizontal
    - and already existing: fade, fromLeft, fromRight, fromTop, fromBottom
